Information
------------------------------

Holiday Horrors: Caught on Camera
Packed full of amazing clips showing what goes wrong when you try to get it away from it all, Holiday Horrors: Caught on Camera might make you never want to take a break again.


1)  Part 1 
Stories include the walk in the woods that became a fight for survival, the world's worst case of sunburn, the dad who ruined his once-in-a-lifetime holiday snaps and the bloke from Wales who became a shark wrestler. Plus, how holidaymakers coped with avalanches, encounters with wild animals - and the most bonkers bank holiday pastimes.

2)  Part 2 
More extraordinary footage sharing what happens when holidays don't go exactly as planned.
Find out the story behind the world's most amazing selfie, one man's miracle escape when his parachute fails to open, Britain's most extreme camper and why tourists are at war with Gibraltar's apes.
Plus amazing clips filmed by holidaymakers who might wished they'd never taken time off work!
